quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  13,19,"E ko on annduﾉ熔 wonnde ko jippinaa kon e maaﾉ預 immorde ka Joomi maa ko goonga, wa'ata wa on ﾉ砥nﾉ熔? Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraaﾉ兎-haqqillaaji ﾉ兎n"
  13,20,"ﾉ兎n hunnooﾉ兎 ahadi Alla ndin, ﾉ兎 firtataa ahodal(hoolaare)"
  13,21,"e ﾉ兎n jokkooﾉ兎 kon ko Alla yamiri yo jokke, hiﾉ兎 hula Joomi maﾉ橡兎, hiﾉ兎 hula bonnde hasboore"
  13,22,"ﾉ兎n muﾃｱﾃｱoriiﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥gol yarluyee Joomi maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiﾉ渡i julde, ﾉ兎 nafqii e kon ko Men arsiki ﾉ兎, gunndoo e kene, hiﾉ兎 duﾃｱira moﾆｴﾆｴere nden bone on. ﾆ‘n ﾉ熔n, no woodani ﾉ兎 battane galle"
  13,23,"Aljannaaji ﾃｱiiﾉ殿l, hiﾉ兎 naata ﾉ擁, e ﾉ兎n moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 e baabiraaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, e rewﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, e geyngolji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n. Hara Malaa'ikaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n hino naatirana ﾉ兎 kala damal"
  13,24,"Kisal wonii e mo'on, sabu muﾃｱal mon ngal. Battane galle ﾉ容n moﾆｴﾆｴii"
  13,25,"ﾆ‘n (non) firtooﾉ兎 ahadi Alla ndin ﾉ殿awo fiﾉ砥gol ndi, hiﾉ兎 taﾆｴoo e ko Alla yamiri kon yo jokke, hiﾉ兎 bonna ka leydi, ﾉ兎 ﾉ熔n, hino woodani ﾉ兎 kuﾉ妖i, hino woodani ﾉ兎 kadi bonﾉ蓉m galle"
  13,26,"Alla no yaﾃｱﾃｱana arsike on Mo O muuyi, Himo ﾉ妬ttina. Hiﾉ兎 weltora nguurndam aduna, nguurndam aduna non wonaali ka laakara, si wanaa dakamme-hoy"
  13,27,"ﾆ‘n yedduﾉ兎 no wi'a: \"Ko haﾉ溶o Aaya jippinee e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?\" Maaku: \"Alla majjinay tun mo O muuyi, O fewna e Makko on tuubuﾉ熔-ruttii"
  13,28,"ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎rﾉ容 mun deeﾆｴirta jantagol Alla. Anndee ko jantagol Alla ngol ﾉ兎rﾉ容 ﾉ容n deeﾆｴirta"
  13,29,"ﾆ‘n gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 golli golle moﾆｴﾆｴe, welo-welo woodaniiﾉ兎 e moﾆｴﾆｴude ruttorde"
  13,30,"Ko wano nii Men nulir-maa e mofte - gomﾉ擁i mofte goo yawtiino ado majje - fii yo a janngan ﾉ兎 nden nde Men wahayini e maaﾉ預, kono hiﾉ兎 yedda Yurmeteeﾉ熔 On. Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni Joomi am. Reweteeﾉ熔 alaa si wanaa Kanko. Ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko kadi woni ruttorde am"
  13,31,"Sinno janngeteende naﾉ妬rano pelle ﾉ容n, maa leydi ndin seekiraa sabu mayre, maa nde wowliniraa maayﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n (harayno ko ndee ﾉ熔o). Ko woni, ko Alla woodani fiyaaku on fow. E gomﾉ擁mﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n anndaali wonnde, sinno Alla muuyuno, O fewnayna denndaangal yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n? Masiibo seeraali no heﾉ妬ra yedduﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ko ﾉ兎 faggitii kon, maa [ngon masiibo] yana takko galle maﾉ橡兎 nden haa fodoore Alla nden ara. Pellet Alla firtataa fodoore"
  13,32,"Gomﾉ擁i Nulaaﾉ兎 jalkitanoo ma ado maaﾉ預. Mi muﾃｱﾃｱanii ﾉ兎n yedduﾉ兎, refti Mi nanngi ﾉ兎. Ko honno lepte Am ﾉ容n wonirnoo"
  13,33,"E hara ko On dariiﾉ熔 e kala wonkii ko ki faggitii kon [ﾉ砥ri hanndude e dewal?...] ﾆ‘ waﾉ預nii Alla kafidii- ﾉ擁. Maaku: \"Innee-ﾉ擁\" Kaa on humpitay Mo ko O anndaa ka leydi? Kaa ko ko [tun] e konngol? Ko woni, heeferﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n cuﾉ擁nanaa ma pewje maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, ﾉ兎 sakkaa(pala) e laawol ngol. Kala mo Alla majjini, fewnoowo alanaa mo"
  13,34,"Hino woodani ﾉ兎 lepte ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet ko lepte laakara ﾉ容n ﾉ砥ri sattude, alanaa ﾉ兎 daﾉ溶doowo (ﾉ兎) e Alla"